article.headline: Harrison's 19 lead Winthrop past Presbyterian 81-71

images.name: Winthrop Eagles vs. Presbyterian Blue Hose: Full Highlights
images.caption: Winthrop Eagles vs. Presbyterian Blue Hose: Full Highlights

article.story: CLINTON, S.C. -- — Kasen Harrison had 19 points in Winthrop's 81-71 victory over Presbyterian on Wednesday night. Harrison was 6 of 8 shooting and 5 of 5 from the free throw line for the Eagles (12-6, 3-0 Big South Conference). Kelton Talford scored 13 points and added six rebounds. Chase Claxton was 3 of 3 shooting and 4 of 4 from the free throw line to finish with 12 points, while adding three steals. The Blue Hose (9-9, 1-2) were led by Samage Teel, who recorded 13 points and four assists. Marquis Barnett added 12 points for Presbyterian. Crosby James also put up 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
